com.poesys.accounting.db.transaction

Class AbstractTransactionFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.poesys.accounting.db.transaction.AbstractTransactionFactory
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    TransactionFactory

    public abstract class AbstractTransactionFactory
extends java.lang.Object

    A separate, sharable set of factory methods for all the transaction classes, including JDBC data-setting, parameter-setting, and primary-key-generation methods. This class is abstract and has a single concrete subclass, TransactionFactory, that you can modify to override the default behavior in the abstract class or implement an as-yet unimplemented method.

    Author:
    Poesys/DB Cartridge
